ClassDef.Name: HttpResponseData

Properties.Name: Success
Properties.Description: Indicates whether the HTTP request completed successfully.

Properties.Name: StatusCode
Properties.Description: The HTTP status code returned by the server.

Properties.Name: Headers
Properties.Description: A table containing the HTTP response headers returned by the server, represented as key-value pairs.

Properties.Name: Body
Properties.Description: The response payload returned by the server as a string buffer.

ClassDef.Description: HttpResponseData represents the result of an HTTP request.
